Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.01,0:22:08.90,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}Always be with you
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.92,0:22:12.88,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}Dear My Friend every day & night
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.52,0:22:16.37,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}Always be with you
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.25,0:22:24.15,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}話しても　まだまだ　足りないまま
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.70,0:22:31.59,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}夕焼けが　街を染めてゆく
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.11,0:22:39.07,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}思うように　なかなか　いかない…って
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.65,0:22:46.79,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}気づいたら　一緒に　泣いていた
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.02,0:22:50.76,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}恋も　夢も　花も　虹も　風も
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.78,0:22:53.32,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}ぜんぶ掴もうよ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.44,0:22:57.11,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}ダイジョウブ！　元気出して
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.17,0:23:01.49,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}私がそばにいるから
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.61,0:23:08.33,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}今日のミス　悔やむより　今　乗り越えて
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.41,0:23:12.07,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}ダイジョウブ！　迷わないで
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.11,0:23:18.20,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}まだ見ぬ未来へと向かって
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.22,0:23:23.28,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}ずっと　歩いてゆこう
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.77,0:23:25.94,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\an7\fs20\fsp0}Dear My Friend every day & night
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.29,0:23:29.85,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\an7\fs20\fsp0}Always be with you
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.25,0:22:24.15,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}話還遠遠沒有說夠
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.70,0:22:31.59,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}晚霞已染紅了街道
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.11,0:22:39.07,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}世事難都如人願
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.65,0:22:46.79,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}察覺時已相依哭泣
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.02,0:22:50.76,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}戀情  夢想  鮮花  彩虹  微風
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.78,0:22:53.32,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}抓緊這一切
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.44,0:22:57.11,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}沒事的  打起精神來
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.17,0:23:01.49,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}因為有我在你的身邊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.61,0:23:08.33,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}與其悔恨今日不如放眼明天
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.41,0:23:12.07,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}沒事的  不要迷惘
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.11,0:23:18.20,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}向著未知的未來
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.22,0:23:23.28,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}永遠走下去
